{"tid":1279174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想講下今日有個有d伏味既投票","createTime":"2019-07-02T15:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T07:54:11.000Z","uid":117585,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"145dd976a77c90875c43d55ed907543666daef63","tid":1279174,"uid":117585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"link係度<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Fvoting.php%3Fid%3D1194&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=4ae310e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1194</a><br />\n<br />\n問題如下：<br />\n反《逃犯條例》修訂抗爭持續，一批示威者昨攻入立法會肆意破壞，你認同此表達訴求的方法嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家見到呢條問題，第一日時間就會投&ldquo;認同&ldquo;<br />\n但再睇真d條問題：<br />\n一批示威者  昨  攻入  立法會  &ldquo;肆意破壞&ldquo;<br />\n伏位就係係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&ldquo;肆意破壞&ldquo;</span></span> 呢4個字<br />\n<br />\n根據漢語網：<a href=\"http://www.chinesewords.org/dict/248739-874.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinesewords.org%2Fdict%2F248739-874.html&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=68502cc9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinesewords.org/dict/248739-874.html</a><br />\n基本釋義： <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任性;任意，肆意掠奪，一小撮犯罪分子肆意擾亂社會治安</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n即係點？即係話你投票認同，就代表你同意示威者係作出左&ldquo;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肆意破壞</span></span>&ldquo;呢個行為，認同示威者係 &ldquo;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一小撮犯罪分子</span></span>&ldquo;。<br />\n<br />\n我想講，呢個投票係由  經濟通X晴報聯合舉辦  ，經濟通同晴報係under香港經濟日報集團，一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">親建制派</span></span>既集團。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我想講，大家下次再遇到呢d投票，要細心睇清楚，唔好幫對家做左助攻都唔知，始終投票結果佢之後點吹點解釋都係佢話事，71之後既輿論戰好緊要，一步都不能夠輸！<br />\n<br />\n中文唔太好，有錯屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea138a04a5dfe31edf372c724da671c8ea6cd503","tid":1279174,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:17:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7efa4ae0ff53e1a5edf5bc9da63ae2630483f7ef","tid":1279174,"uid":246980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fd45dfabaf5768967de6adcb677c4f639613356","tid":1279174,"uid":203889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:28:46.000Z","msg":"佢開得呢個投票<br />\n其實無論結果點都係任佢吹<br />\n因為係專登"},{"pid":"3c8dff5a1f13ea666bb3d68cbcaa7189730502b1","tid":1279174,"uid":117585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:43:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a3adc26a2e0a25382f042ff051124ee0a592802","tid":1279174,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}